{"view":"article","slug":"4x4-yau","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"四阶Yau法 (邱)"},"content":{"zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>四阶Yau法 (邱)</strong></p><p>由Robert Yau提出</p><p><strong>符号</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p><p>外层</p></td><td><p><strong>r</strong></p><p>两层</p></td><td><p><strong>2R</strong></p><p>内层</p></td><td><p><strong>3r</strong></p><p>三层</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F2C (两个对心)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>第二心</strong></p><p>对其他情况, 见\"四阶后二心\"页.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') r U' r'\">(U') r U' r'</span></p><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"U r U2' r'\">U r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"(U') r U' r'\">(U') r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F3E (三个底棱)</strong></p><p>z转体将白心放在L面. 用外层转动将一对白棱放到2L和2R层, 然后用r转动让它们合并, 接着将该棱的白贴纸放在L面. 用同样的步骤再还原两对白棱. 要保证这三对白棱的相对位置是正确的.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>r [U]</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r2 [U']\">r2 [U']</span></p></td><td><p><strong>1个已还原</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3个已还原</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L4C (后四心)</strong></p><p>在L4C阶段, 始终将左手大拇指和中指分别放在F和B面的十字棱 (假设第三个十字棱在DL). r, 3r, U流还原L4C.<a id=\"_Hlk5989805\"></a> 保证所有心的相对位置是正确的. 还原完F心 (第三心), 做x', 还原当前F心 (第四心) , 做x', 还原当前F心 (第五心), 第六心就会自动还原. 也可以还原U心, 然后做x.下面是还原F心的一般思路. 紫色强调不能破坏的棱.</p><p><strong>还原F面左棒</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U' 3r'\">3r U' 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U 3r'\">3r U 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'\">3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>已还原</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F心 (</strong> <strong>r,U流)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U r'\">r U r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>已还原</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>LCE (末底棱)</strong></p><p>做z', 然后将LCE放在E层. 合并完后将该棱正确地放在底层.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R U R') u\">u' (R U R') u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R U R' F R' F' R) u\">u' (R U R' F R' F' R) u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u2 (R U R') u2\">u2 (R U R') u2</span></p></td><td><p><strong>已还原</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L8E 323法 (后八棱)</strong></p><p>做u', 将3对棱放到E层, 使得做u后, 它们会合并好. 之后, 仅用2个<a href=\"/alg/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a>槽来合并剩余5对棱, 每次做2到3对.</p><p><strong>标准实例</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u'</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U L y'\">L' U L y'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"y' R U R' F R' F' R\">y' R U R' F R' F' R</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u'</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"F R' F' R\">F R' F' R</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"u' U'\">u' U'</span></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image80.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image82.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><br>三阶</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk5989991\"></a><strong>三阶上不可能的特殊情况</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>O特</strong></p><p>奇翻棱</p></td><td><p><strong>P特</strong></p><p>奇置换</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image84.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image86.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'\">r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"alg-chip\" data-alg=\"r2 R2' U2 2R2 u2 2R2 u2 [U2]\">r2 R2' U2 2R2 u2 2R2 u2 [U2]</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["(U') r U' r'","U r U2' r'","r U' r'","r U2' r'","r2 [U']","3r U' 3r'","3r U 3r'","3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'","r U r'","u' (R U R') u","u' (R U R' F R' F' R) u","u2 (R U R') u2","R U' R'","L' U L y'","y' R U R' F R' F' R","F R' F' R","u' U'","r U2 x r U2 (r U2' r' U2) l U2 (r' U2' r U2) r' U2' r'","r2 R2' U2 2R2 u2 2R2 u2 [U2]"],"thumb":"/stats/alg/media/4x4-yau/zh/image2.svg","warningCount":1,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
